4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals looking to become cybersecurity specialists without prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, capped at 16 students per class. Participants will build foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration while mastering cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The bootcamp culminates in an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, acknowledged by various institutions. Courses are available in both English and Spanish, with no prerequisites for enrollment. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop